Package me.andrew28.addons.conquer.api

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    PowerHolder
    Represents something that can hold power
    SerializableToFields
    Represents something that can be serialized down to Fields
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConquerClaim<T>
    A claim which can be represented by an object (usually a Chunk)
    ConquerFaction
    A faction which is usually a group of multiple players
    ConquerPlayer
    An offline or online player that may or may not be in a ConquerFaction
    EventForwarder
    All implementations of this class which will use EventForwarder.callEvent(Event) to "translate" implementation specific events to Conquer ones like ConquerFactionCreateEvent.
    FactionResolver
    A class which allows you to resolve factions through a variety of ways
    FactionsPlugin
    The base class for any Factions plugin implementation
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ClaimType
    Types of a ConquerClaim
    ConquerPlayer.Role
    The role an ConquerPlayer may have in their faction
    Relation
    Represents the relationship between two entities like two ConquerFactions
